        About this item

        • New trendy toy furniture The kids floor sofa set includes 2 basic parts overall56.7"x28.3"x17.3"2 triangle wedges (19.7"x12.6"x9.4"), 2 semi-circular handrails (8.7" x 28.3") for free assembly.
        • Selected material for kids Jela modular furniture adapts premium eco-friendly and nontoxic material to care your kids health with soft touch sense. The whole product has been passed CertiPUR-US which prohibits any CFCs use, or any harmful elements through the whole manufacturing.
        • Unleash children's creativity The 8pcs kids sofa set can be free combined up to your innovative creative idea such as tree house, reading cornerlittle playhouseplay table, etc. Build an infinitely creative play land on their own and shine your every home interior! Easy to set up and collect Best Zippers make setup quick and smooth. The high-density polyurethane foam ensures you easy to storage and bounce back completely like first time.
        • A warm interactive space for family The kids couch set creates a real fantastic scene to increase interactive activity for a whole family. You will get more chance to accompany your kids to enjoy their little world! Nice packaging & stellar service The 8pcs modular kids sofa come with nice shipping and package to avoid damage. Any query please feel free to contact us and we will reply immediately.
        • Please Note: The kids play couches combine the function of sofa couch and building forts. Especially designed for kids exploring, all the parts are modular and removable . We recommend customers who only need the adult sofa couch function should use it against wall to keep it more fixed. PLEASE CHECK DIMENSION BEFORE YOUR PURCHASE.

        2. About Us

          Hi, we are jela.

          jela is a relatively young but fast-developing brand whose products are popular in most North American countries. Whether kid's play couch, baby climbing blocks, or memory foam products, each piece is constructed with the customer's comfort in mind.

          Our mission is to continuously improve children's happiness and be loved by kids. We hope that our little efforts have brought joy to your children and the whole family.

        3. Jela Kids Couch Explorer Sofa

        Product Description

        Medium 8pcs kids play couch

        Jela kids couch more love, care, creativity for your beloved kids

        Jela has more than 20 years experience as an expert manufacturing kids couches. This modular foam kids couch is designed to combine the function of comfortable rest and provoking kids interests from building different playroom shapes , such as a reading corner, castles, happy hammock, the gamer place, cozy cave, reading nook, tree house, etc. It is an easy way to keep your kids nature at home, also creating a warm atmosphere with a whole big family.

        JELA cares for kids health, we are trying to offer more love for kids with a reassuring way. So we adopt highest quiality material that is soft to touch, products have all been passed CertiPUR-US which prohibits any CFCs use, no smell, non toxic, the fabric has been passed friction test through ten thousands times without pillings. We are always dedicated to offering better and selective products to our kids and family decor.

        Specific details of kids couch

        High density to rebounce

        High density sponge, quickly bounce back as original shape once you recieve it. After compressed by certained machine, it can still be fluffy even stayed in box more than 12months!

        Sleek fabric texture

        Modern and sleek fabric with soft touch sense, no pilling after friction. Less maintenance and still be upscale even for years use.

        No sharp edges/ smooth zippers

        Doubling stitching arround all zippers, will not tear up easily. we adpot best zipper and make sure it is smooth when you get quick collect and remove. Saving your time and energy!

        Q: What does it mean when I see the CertiPUR-US name or logo associated with a product?

        A: It means the foam in the bedding or upholstered furniture has been tested to meet CertiPUR-US rigorous standards for emissions, content, performance, and durability. Specifically, the foam is:

        • Made without ozone depleters
        • Made without PBDEs or the following Tris flame retardants: TCEP, TDBPP, TDCPP or TEPA
        • Made without mercury, lead and heavy metals
        • Made without formaldehyde
        • Made without phthalates regulated by the Consumer Product Safety Commission
        • Low VOC (Volatile Organic Compound) emissions for indoor air quality (less than 0.5 parts per million)

            How customer reviews and ratings work

            Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

            To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
